Officer, Department of Soil and Water Conservation, Chhatrapati
Department of Soil and Water Conservation,
Government Order No: Establishment-2023 / No.289 (Part-I) / Order No. 1 / Water - 2
Mr. Vasant Baburao Galfade, Regional Water Conservation Officer, Soil and Water Conservation Department,
Under this order of Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar, the Maharashtra Regulation of Transfer of Government Employees and Prevention of Delay in the discharge of Government Duties Act, 2005, 4 (4) and 4 (5),
As per the provision, transfers are being made on administrative grounds with the approval of the competent authorities.
Mr. Galfade is being transferred and posted as Superintendent Engineer and Deputy Secretary (Architecture), Department of Soil and Water Conservation, Mantralaya, Mumbai.
The Government Order is available on the Government's website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
